            <p><img alt="Download icon" class="inline-icon" src="https://static.jboss.org/rhd/fonts/images_design_RHDev_homepage_download-3.svg" /> Get immediate access to<b> download</b> Red Hat® products</p>

            <p><img alt="Download icon" class="inline-icon" src="https://static.jboss.org/rhd/fonts/images_design_RHDev_homepage_cloud-3.svg" /> Launch your new apps in the<b> cloud</b> on Red Hat® OpenShift</p>

            <p><img alt="Download icon" class="inline-icon" src="https://static.jboss.org/rhd/fonts/images_design_RHDev_homepage_lowercost-3.svg" /> Offers and<b> discounts</b> on products, services, training, &amp; events</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

